chinese: 给，传递；通过 n，飞机或人造卫星等的一次掠过
把棒子递给我
以推测，猜测；投机，做投机买卖
他们在推测他们的同事为什么难过。
english: They are speculating about why their colleague is upset

chinese: adj.合得来的
他和他的朋友很合得来，因为他们有相似的兴趣和观点。
english: He is compatible with his friend, because of their similar interests and opinions

chinese: v. 生产，制造 几，制造业；（复数）产
这家工厂用机器制造产品。
english: This factory uses machines to manufacture goods

chinese: V. 按，压n.新闻界
按下这个红色的按钮门就会打开。
english: Press the red button and the door will open

chinese: adj， 本地的，本国的；与生俱来的 .当地动植物
印第安人是美国的原住民。
english: American Indians are the people native to the United States

chinese: （使）相关联
这张图表显示，收入水平与教育水平相关联。
english: The chart shows that level of income correlates with the level of education

chinese: v. 唤起
他新的一天从被闹钟唤醒开始。
english: Being aroused from sleep is the beginning of his day

chinese: n. 橄榄；橄榄树 adj，橄榄色的
最好的烹饪油是用橄榄制作的。
english: The best cooking oil is made from olives

chinese: n.寄生虫；靠他人为生的人
臭虫是一种可怕的寄生虫，它们靠吸血生存。
english: Bedbugs are a kind of horrible parasite, they feed on human blood

chinese: n.精致；优雅
这道甜品精致和美味兼具。
english: The dessert has both delicacy and deliciousness

chinese: 吐.尽（力），运用，发挥
我用尽全力拾起这些箱子。
english: I exerted all my strength to lift all the boxes

chinese: adj.奇异的，不寻常的；古怪的，诡异
这些根茎类蔬菜看起来非常奇怪。
english: These root vegetables look so weird

chinese: ad）.联邦政府的；联邦制的
美国联邦政府的中心就在这座建筑内。
english: The center of the federal government of the United States is in this building

chinese: m.党羽；虔诚信徒 ad）.偏袒的；盲目推崇的
这两个党派尝试着合作而非竞争。
english: These two partisans attempt to cooperate with each other rather than competing

chinese: m.演讲者，讲师
讲师正在给很多听众做演讲。
english: The lecturer is giving a speech to a large audience
